snippet.title: Chenso Club: A Cute But Deadly 2D Platform Brawler | gamescom 2022
snippet.description:
Using chainsaws, hammers, and the aliens’ own life force against them - these fearless warriors will pulverize enemies on their way to victory in this action-packed, side-scrolling platform brawler!

#IGN #ChensoClub
